## Part 3: EduPod Data Readiness Assessment

### 3.1 What EduPod Already Has

| Regulatory Need | EduPod Module | Data Available | Gap |
|----------------|---------------|----------------|-----|
| September Returns File A (staff) | Staff Profiles + Payroll | Staff records, qualifications, employment type, hours | DES-specific field mappings, encryption |
| September Returns File C (classes) | Classes | Class sizes, year groups | DES format compliance |
| September Returns File D (subjects) | Academics (Subjects) | Subject list with types | DES subject code mapping |
| September Returns File E (students) | Students | Full student records | DES format, PPSN handling |
| Form TL (teacher hours) | Scheduling | Teacher hours by subject already tracked | Auto-generation formatter |
| Tusla SAR | Attendance | Cumulative absence tracking, pattern detection | Tusla absence codes, SAR export format |
| Tusla AAR | Attendance | Aggregate attendance data | AAR format |
| Tusla suspensions/expulsions | Behaviour (Sanctions + Exclusions) | Suspension lifecycle, exclusion cases | Reduced School Day tracking |
| Child Safeguarding | Behaviour (Safeguarding) | Tusla/Garda referrals, sealed records, DLP | Compliance dashboard surfacing |
| Anti-Bullying | Behaviour (Incidents) | Incident recording, categorisation | Bí Cineálta categories, Board report template |
| FSSU | Finance | Chart of accounts, transaction records | FSSU standardised format mapping |
| GDPR | Compliance | SARs, erasure, rectification, audit logs | Already built — surface in portal |
| Inspectorate data | Reports/Analytics | Cross-module analytics, KPI dashboard | WSE-specific aggregation |
| Admissions notices | Admissions | Application pipeline, stats | Annual Notice template |

### 3.2 Key Gaps to Fill

1. **DES file format specifications** — Need exact format specs for Files A–E (likely obtained through DES/vendor consultation or reverse-engineering from competitors)
2. **DES encryption standard** — Files are auto-encrypted; need the specific encryption method and keys
3. **P-POD API/sync protocol** — Contact `ppodhelpdesk@education.gov.ie` for vendor integration specs
4. **POD API/sync protocol** — Contact POD helpdesk for primary school integration specs
5. **Tusla portal export format** — SAR electronic submission format specification
6. **DES subject code master list** — Canonical subject code list for DTR sync
7. **PPSN handling** — Secure storage and transmission of Personal Public Service Numbers
8. **Reduced School Day tracking** — New data point needed in attendance/student record
9. **CBA assessment type** — Junior Cycle specific assessment workflow
10. **SLAR meeting management** — Teacher moderation meeting orchestration

