## Part 7: External Dependencies & Next Steps

### 7.1 Information to Obtain from DES/External Bodies

| Item | Source | Priority |
|------|--------|----------|
| September Return file format specifications | DES / reverse-engineer from VSware docs | Critical |
| Encryption standard for Files A–E | DES | Critical |
| P-POD API/sync protocol | `ppodhelpdesk@education.gov.ie` | Critical |
